  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of the study is to determine whether psychological therapy (self-help or
      individualized intense stress management) is different than a single drug treatment in terms
      of their effectiveness for lowering blood pressure.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
